{
  "stem": "6763.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were-- from what I remember-- and this is very timely because of the times that we're going through right now-- is the-- they were persecuting the Serbs, who were fighting to surrender to the Germans [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] very vigorously, right from the beginning.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But coming back, these two men came in uniform, black uniforms-- black leather coats and boots and black hats-- and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] literally sent chills through me at this point because I knew exactly what was happening.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They came out and very politely approached, rang the doorbell, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] asked for my father.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they identified themselves, that they were from the SS, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] that within three days we should be at the railroad station in Zagreb.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And that's basically the beginning of--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were no other Jews in the area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I, basically, through my growing years, almost-- from very rare occasions, I was the only Jew in many, many places.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was just the nature of the-- because we never lived in a ghetto or, you know, in an environment where we were living with a homogeneous group of people.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they discussed it with us-- with us children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, look, you know, you're going to have to pack some things, and, you know, make it the important things.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we have to report.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We don't know what the future will hold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We don't know where we're going, but we're going to try our very best to be together.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father had this reassuring quality about him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We said, OK, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
